subject: Lacrosse
lead_paragraph: Several members of the Duke women's lacrosse team warmed up for their N.C.A.A. semifinal wearing sweatbands with the numbers of three men's players accused of rape — a more qualified statement of support than the "Innocent" headbands they said they would wear.
